{"tid":480701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無發覺窮人特別鐘意生仔？","createTime":"2017-11-26T11:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T14:51:02.000Z","uid":42407,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"17fb5cacf9efdb59ad88ebea49c8cf34d0ac780c","tid":480701,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"有3,4個細路嘅家庭多數都係窮<br />\n係咪因為窮人除左扑野無野好做？無錢還套？"},{"pid":"a40746bbeb736456dea09aa9b5e54bae475a678c","tid":480701,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有3,4個細路嘅家庭多數都係窮<br />\n係咪因為窮人除左扑野無野好做？無錢<span style=\"color: red;\">買</span>套？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"83422c79c74bc9a623ff980ac367ab8fd6c37e63","tid":480701,"uid":21558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T12:26:45.000Z","msg":"唔生多幾個，點拎多啲綜援？<br />\n點拎大間啲既公屋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要搏下仔女有一兩個係成材<br />\n女既嫁有錢仔<br />\n男既娶有錢女添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83152c874edccee91b9761d8295ba28ebff2bb7f","tid":480701,"uid":52539,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:01:46.000Z","msg":"仲要唔識教/唔教 果下先最死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有D就美其名比自由D細路 實際就自己懶理 自己走去行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一句讀書係自己既KO一切 <br />\n想學野 補習? 冇錢WO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀書既野 EG英文默書想搵父母幫手?<br />\n唔識WO 自己搞掂啦~比左錢學校嫁喇 問老師啦<br />\n最後讀唔成書?你問題啦 怪得邊個丫<br />\n係咁冇資源既環境下入到神科 有既 0.0001%神人囉<br />\n連基本既錢 仲邊有心情讀書丫 <br />\n早餐都冇得你食啦 餓住番學 日日番去訓教<br />\n不過依家都好D 起馬有手機 可以下載一堆學習APP 真係要好好利用<br />\n以前?查字典都查撚到你死<br />\n<br />\n有錢既或知識都有番咁上下既仔女一定有番咁上下<br />\n過往香港咁多個神童好多都係父母係老師黎<br />\n有錢請人補習果D就唔洗講啦"},{"pid":"d8f25f8d3116eb03a18d88600e402160df64fffd","tid":480701,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"唔生多 d 點攞多 d 綜援呀"},{"pid":"34435703666d0e772f1bffd41b3fd4bf3fba7c95","tid":480701,"uid":1790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"沒娛樂 屋企逼 沒冷氣 <br />\n根本係扑野良機"},{"pid":"eb853bc022b3ab660b82e0cf355f58e1864159cc","tid":480701,"uid":160050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"生仔只係副作用<br />\n享受生產過程<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26b529fcd7c0c48aaba503a179951456d0079f2","tid":480701,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"mark six"},{"pid":"ecf6f6a6378575304b599cb5290069a02df2fc52","tid":480701,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5494b0c30edeecc2e7d6dc4990df54009aaf3b0c","tid":480701,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:03:48.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"0004b2e7b6ea41b36fddceb937fc593d7d382245","tid":480701,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:05:39.000Z","msg":"生多d<br />\n總會生到個搵錢多嘅"},{"pid":"dc78973cacce58a0737dc947bf62f43c210d1750","tid":480701,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:06:54.000Z","msg":"窮到condom都無錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0e97dcc27b83cb3bdf66034ac9313ea30443f5","tid":480701,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生多d<br />\n總會生到個搵錢多嘅</blockquote><br />\n其他又咪受苦"}]}